casebody.data: In the MATTER OF DISCIPLINE OF Glenn D. DESANTIS. No. D-3061 Supreme Court of the United States. Feb. 24, 2020 Glenn D. DeSantis, of Voorhees, New Jersey, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court, and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
